journelText:
I have encountered a most strange being today. It appears to be a small rodent, dragging a slice of bread covered in cheese and some kind of red sause. As I watched, it drawed the strange foodstuff onto what my trall informed me was a landmine. [PAGE BREAK] For a moment I ruminated on how I should proceed.

Finally, I made a decided to:
[BUTTON](Scenario_Test_2_a){I strode forward and snatched up the rodent so as to drain the life from it.}

[BUTTON](Scenario_Test_2_b){I instructed my thrall to shoo the rodent away and retrieve the landmine.}
